It's new and it's Opal

Our Ranges

OPAL DIRECT

   Exclusive collections at entry-level prices
   The Opal Direct department contains 4 low-cost collections. The Opal
   Direct catalogue is issued every 3 months and shows full collections,
   including new items.
   SEE MORE

OPAL LICENSING

   Children’s and teenagers’ licensed collections.
   As European leader in the children’s glasses market, Opal’s owes its
   success to a well-chosen brand portfolio and its in-house creativity.
   SEE MORE

OPAL STUDIO

   Exclusive collections
   With all its design know-how and expertise in sourcing, Opal is able to
   create glasses collections that offer excellent value at the best
   possible price.
   SEE MORE

